WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:05.200
It was aight o'clock in the morning, and the red hot sun was burning bright.

2
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:11.500
The sky was blue, and the air dry. As it was already heating up.

3
00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:15.100
Just when he woke up the lazy boy heard his mother call.

4
00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:22.800
"Yes... I'm awake! I'll be down soon, just give me one minute!" he replied.

5
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:29.900
His pet, a black cat, was sitting at the leg of the bed, as if he wanted to say: "Goodmorning".


6
00:00:29.900 --> 00:00:40.200
"I have no time to play with you now" said the boy. "I need to go to the bathroom to take a shower and wash my self".

